node.text: Charles Bukowski is the first poet I related to and loved. His novels and poetry books gave me countless hours of connection to my highest self. Happy birthday to the mighty Buk, you are immortal and I love you.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Flea on August 15, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text: Thank you to MHA nation and all the tribes at the Little Shell powwow this weekend. It was amazing and inspiring, I’m reeling from the colors, the interstellar singing and drumming and dancing the likes of which I’ve never seen before. A portal to the cosmos, the voices of the ancestors ringing clear and true. I was honored by Trae Little Sky to wear his regalia, and dance in the grand entry, it meant the world to me. All my respect and gratitude.
